FT  12 AUG 93 / People: Arjo Wiggins Appleton
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Arjo Wiggins Appleton has appointed the distinguished, if media shy, Italian
industrialist Gabriele Galateri to its board as a non-executive director,
replacing Pierre Dufournier, who has retired.
Galateri is managing director of IFIL, a diversified holding company which
